igh-growth business that offers competitive compensation in a creative, flexible environment that invests in its professionals. Our new senior DevOps engineer will be working working with a new infrastructure, that is Serverless first. Currently we are fully migrated to microservices.",{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":66,"children":67},{},[68],{"type":40,"value":69},"Join us, it will be fun!",{"type":26,"tag":27,"props":71,"children":73},{"id":72},"whats-in-it-for-you",[74],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":75,"children":76},{},[77],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":78,"children":79},{},[80],{"type":40,"value":81},"What’s in it for you",{"type":26,"tag":83,"props":84,"children":85},"ol",{},[86,92,97,102,107,112],{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":88,"children":89},"li",{},[90],{"type":40,"value":91},"Work with the latest and greatest technologies.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":93,"children":94},{},[95],{"type":40,"value":96},"Learn from the best people. We constantly challenge the status quo, learn from each other, and invent new ways of building a great product.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":98,"children":99},{},[100],{"type":40,"value":101},"We actually write automated tests. We take advantage of the latest automation tools like automatic deployments, CI/CD pipelines, and more.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":103,"children":104},{},[105],{"type":40,"value":106},"Work remotely in the comfort of your home or a shared co-working space.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":108,"children":109},{},[110],{"type":40,"value":111},"Work on challenging problems, innovate, and have fun while doing it.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":113,"children":114},{},[115],{"type":40,"value":116},"Travel around the world. We offer occasional business trips to work with our clients face-to-face from their offices.",{"type":26,"tag":27,"props":118,"children":120},{"id":119},"required-qualifications",[121],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":122,"children":123},{},[124],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":125,"children":126},{},[127],{"type":40,"value":128},"Required Qualifications",{"type":26,"tag":83,"props":130,"children":131},{},[132,137,142,147,152,157,162,167],{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":133,"children":134},{},[135],{"type":40,"value":136},"7+ years of professional full-time experience working as a DevOps.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":138,"children":139},{},[140],{"type":40,"value":141},"5+ years of professional full-time experience with AWS.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":143,"children":144},{},[145],{"type":40,"value":146},"1+yearsofexperiencewithNode.js.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":148,"children":149},{},[150],{"type":40,"value":151},"1+ years of experience with Terraform or similar IaC tools.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":153,"children":154},{},[155],{"type":40,"value":156},"Experience with deploying modern logging system from the ground up",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":158,"children":159},{},[160],{"type":40,"value":161},"On-call rotation availability.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":163,"children":164},{},[165],{"type":40,"value":166},"Experience managing IAM roles.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":168,"children":169},{},[170],{"type":40,"value":171},"Experience with best security practices.",{"type":26,"tag":27,"props":173,"children":175},{"id":174},"nice-to-haves",[176],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":177,"children":178},{},[179],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":180,"children":181},{},[182],{"type":40,"value":183},"Nice to haves",{"type":26,"tag":83,"props":185,"children":186},{},[187,192,197],{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":188,"children":189},{},[190],{"type":40,"value":191},"A formal Computer Science degree.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":193,"children":194},{},[195],{"type":40,"value":196},"Kubernetes experience",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":198,"children":199},{},[200],{"type":40,"value":201},"Load testing experience",{"type":26,"tag":27,"props":203,"children":205},{"id":204},"frequently-asked-questions",[206],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":207,"children":208},{},[209],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":210,"children":211},{},[212],{"type":40,"value":213},"Frequently Asked Questions",{"type":26,"tag":215,"props":216,"children":217},"blockquote",{},[218],{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":219,"children":220},{},[221],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":222,"children":223},{},[224],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":225,"children":226},{},[227],{"type":40,"value":228},"What are your typical clients?",{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":230,"children":231},{},[232],{"type":40,"value":233},"The majority of our clients are venture-backed startups in the growth stage. Usually, at this stage, the company already achieved a product-market fit and is looking to expand rapidly. That’s where we bring the best engineering practices, strong architecture, and the latest technologies to help companies scale.",{"type":26,"tag":215,"props":235,"children":236},{},[237],{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":238,"children":239},{},[240],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":241,"children":242},{},[243],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":244,"children":245},{},[246],{"type":40,"value":247},"What is the length of your engagements?",{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":249,"children":250},{},[251],{"type":40,"value":252},"Most of our long-term full-time engagements last multiple years so you are able to grow your career with the company you are currently working in.",{"type":26,"tag":215,"props":254,"children":255},{},[256],{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":257,"children":258},{},[259],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":260,"children":261},{},[262],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":263,"children":264},{},[265],{"type":40,"value":266},"What’s your company size?",{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":268,"children":269},{},[270],{"type":40,"value":271},"The Right Balance team has 60+ engineers going to 100+ by the end of the year. It’s exciting to be a part of a solid engineering team making meaningful contributions.",{"type":26,"tag":215,"props":273,"children":274},{},[275],{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":276,"children":277},{},[278],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":279,"children":280},{},[281],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":282,"children":283},{},[284],{"type":40,"value":285},"What happens if the engagement is completed?",{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":287,"children":288},{},[289],{"type":40,"value":290},"Most of our engagements are long-term in nature. That said, if the current engagement is ramping down, we’ll present you with more long-term opportunities to transition into.",{"type":26,"tag":215,"props":292,"children":293},{},[294],{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":295,"children":296},{},[297],{"type":26,"tag":32,"props":298,"children":299},{},[300],{"type":26,"tag":36,"props":301,"children":302},{},[303],{"type":40,"value":304},"What are your core values?",{"type":26,"tag":306,"props":307,"children":308},"ul",{},[309,314,319],{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":310,"children":311},{},[312],{"type":40,"value":313},"Client First: we only win when our clients win. We treat client challenges as our own.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":315,"children":316},{},[317],{"type":40,"value":318},"Ownership: we embrace responsibility, taking on challenges, getting them to completion, and enjoying getting things done.",{"type":26,"tag":87,"props":320,"children":321},{},[322],{"type":40,"value":323},"Quality: we’re passionate about achieving quality outcomes by applying meticulous attention to detail.",{"title":7,"searchDepth":325,"depth":325,"links":326},2,[327,328,329,330,331,332],{"id":29,"depth":325,"text":41},{"id":50,"depth":325,"text":59},{"id":72,"depth":325,"text":81},{"id":119,"depth":325,"text":128},{"id":174,"depth":325,"text":183},{"id":204,"depth":325,"text":213},"markdown","content:opportunities:senior-devops-engineer-1.md","content","opportunities/senior-devops-engineer-1.md","md",1707100100849]